title: Texas Public Information Act Request: Austin Day Spa (Texas Department Of Public Safety) (Texas Department Of Public Safety)

communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Texas Public Information Act, I hereby request the following records:

Pursuant to the Texas Public Information Act, I hereby request the following records:

1) Records relating to "Austin Day Spa", a health spa located at 2206 Hidalgo st, Austin, TX 78702, since January 1, 2020.
2) Records records pertaining to the address 2206 Hidalgo st, Austin, TX 78702 since January 1, 2020.

To minimize the scope of the search, please limit to:
1) Correspondence records pertaining to the above
2) Complaint or investigation records pertaining to the above

It's possible that this business will appear in documents pertaining to sex trafficking.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

Sincerely,
